summary: Adds a small House near Fort Amol with a small backstory.
descriptionHtml:
I made a small House near Fort Amol with a small backhistory. You can take the house as a Player home. Inside you can find:
>1 Bookshelf (3x18 Books)
>1 Bed, Table, Chairs, Chimney, Shelves, small Loot. (Its a common house)
>A cave


Requires: Skyrim^^


Soon i will improve the details of the cave interior (I don\'t like it yet)
I plan to add a small side quest for this location in the future.
Feel free to make suggestions.


Known Bugs: No, but in the interiors is no navmesh yet
author: bronzeP
